metadata.name: Mint Pass
metadata.description:
Mint passes are the first step to redeeming a Battle.town-ready Grailed PUMA Slipstream NFT and a matching pair of 1:1 physical sneakers.

Must hold a Grailed Slipstream-supported PFP to craft and redeem. 

Visit [official site](https://www.grailedpuma.xyz) for more information.
